General.Name: Mont Royal Resources Ltd
General.Description: Mont Royal Resources Limited engages in the mineral exploration business in Canada. The company explores for gold, copper, silver, and nickel deposits. It holds interests in the Wapatik project that includes 220 claims covering an area of 115 square kilometers located in the James Bay-Eeyou Istchee region, Quebec; and the Northern Lights Minerals projects situated in Quebec, Canada. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
